    </div>
    <div class="pca">
      <p class="sub-title">Approach</p>
      <p>The hotel, comprising 6 rooms, centered its concept around Wagashi - Japanese sweets. Each room was themed after a specific type of sweet, with carefully curated objects complementing the theme and characteristics of the building.</p>
