    <div class="pca">
      <p class="sub-title">Challenge</p>
      <p>For the new hotel, Nazuna Kyoto Gosho, we partnered with a local family-owned operator. However, their initial branding required a refresh to align with Kiraku's vision for luxury hotel developments. The challenge was to craft a timeless brand identity that could encompass all properties managed under the Nazuna family name.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pca">
      <p class="sub-title">Approach</p>
      <p>The primary objective of the brand identity was to evoke timelessness and mirror the characteristics and ambiance of the old historical buildings housing the hotels. This led to the incorporation of clean lines and the selection of classic-like serif fonts for a sophisticated touch.</p>
